## Complete DST variable list

To get the complete DST variable list, click [this link](https://github.com/steno-aarhus/registers-project-database/blob/main/dst/registers-and-variables/709627_variabelliste_20250811.xlsx). 

This will take you to an Excel file on GitHub.com with the complete variable list. To download the file, click the download button ![](/images/download-icon.svg) in the top right corner of the page.

## Registers from Statistics Denmark

Below you will find a full describtion of all DST registers and variables in the project database
